				<td colspan="2"><span>Thanks for all the replies folks.  While I can't say that I'm enjoying the bug, it does make me feel a little bit better to know that its a widespread problem, and I'm not going insane.
<br />

<br />
From the replies it sounds like there are no real good ways to combat the bug, or even to work around it (snaring and pre-meleeing haven't worked at all for me).  It also sounds like there are no zones which are immune.
<br />

<br />
I guess I'll just keep my fingers crossed that SoE fixes the problem soonish.  Playing a very group dependant character as my main, cleric, it was very nice to be able to log my bard on for a few minutes at a time and not have the worry of needing to track down a group and make a long term commitment.
<br />

